divs: Sighting DetailsI work for a wharehouse in south of chandler, Az. as i was leaving my workplace for the day, i noticed this strange object just above the tree line. At first glance, i thought it was some type of remote control airship, but it was motionless and to big and looked to sinister, a sudden chill ran up and down my spine, it was very eerie, i ran to my vehicle nearby to get my camera, i snapped one picture as fast as posibble, as i was going to snap another it disappeared, almost like when you turn a tv switch off, "very strange". If you look almost in the center of the picture, you can see three construction workers unawhere of the situation, going about everyday worklife.
